 nonnegative. These bounds are all slight\nimprovements of previously known ones, and are simply achieved by proper\ninitialization of the $f$-factor algorithm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Nov 2016 21:22:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-24"}
