ent an overview of the exciting opportunities that\nlie ahead to further understand the fundamentals of novel spin physics,\nopportunities offered by the appearance of diffraction limited storage rings\nand free electron lasers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Nov 2016 08:52:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 19 Dec 2016 14:10:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-27"}
