ver we show\nthat the Dirac operator of the split Dirac structure is related to a Lorentzian\nversion of a discretization of the Dirac operator introduced earlier by\nMarcolli and van Suijlekom.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Nov 2016 15:28:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-24"}
